| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2287 — Recovery Inhibition (raworld)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0ecc8233-88e9-5b0e-9937-abbf54bbde9d"
